<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Support Ticket Created</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F46E5 0%, #7C3AED 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .ticket-number {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #4F46E5;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #4338CA;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .ticket-details {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .ticket-details dt {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .ticket-details dd {
      margin: 0 0 12px 0;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .sla-info {
      background: #ecfdf5;
      border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>üé´ Support Ticket Created</h1>
    <div class="ticket-number">#{{ticketNumber}}</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for contacting CAFEelevate Support. We've received your request and our team is on it!</p>
    
    <dl class="ticket-details">
      <dt>Ticket Number</dt>
      <dd><strong>#{{ticketNumber}}</strong></dd>
      
      <dt>Subject</dt>
      <dd>{{subject}}</dd>
      
      <dt>Category</dt>
      <dd>{{category}}</dd>
      
      <dt>Priority</dt>
      <dd>{{priority}}</dd>
      
      <dt>Status</dt>
      <dd>Open - Awaiting Response</dd>
    </dl>
    
    <div class="sla-info">
      <strong>‚è∞ Response Time:</strong> Our support team will respond within <strong>24 hours</strong> during business hours (Mon-Fri, 9 AM - 6 PM).
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{ticketUrl}}" class="button">View Ticket Status</a>
    </div>
    
    <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>A support specialist will review your request</li>
      <li>You'll receive an email when they respond</li>
      <li>You can track progress and reply via the ticket portal</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p><strong>Need to add more information?</strong> Simply reply to this email or visit your ticket page.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p><strong>Ticket Reference:</strong> #{{ticketNumber}}</p>
    <p>For urgent issues, call our support line: +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
    <p>CAFEelevate Support Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
